com.extjs.gxt.ui.client.image
Interface XImages

All Superinterfaces:
com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.ImageBundle
All Known Subinterfaces:
AccessImages, GrayImages
public interface XImages
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.ImageBundle

Defines the icons used by the Ext GWT library.

To 'override' these images extend this interface, override the desired methods and add a @Resource annotation.
